{"data":{"id":"ChIJc-W9TRbM1IkRfrv7IR-gtT0","types":["dentist","point_of_interest","health","establishment"],"formattedAddress":"2215 Danforth Ave, Toronto, ON M4C 1K3, Canada","rating":4.6,"websiteUri":"https://www.mainsquaredental.ca/","regularOpeningHours":{"openNow":false,"periods":[{"open":{"day":1,"hour":9,"minute":0},"close":{"day":1,"hour":18,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":2,"hour":9,"minute":0},"close":{"day":2,"hour":18,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":3,"hour":9,"minute":0},"close":{"day":3,"hour":18,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":4,"hour":9,"minute":0},"close":{"day":4,"hour":18,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":5,"hour":9,"minute":0},"close":{"day":5,"hour":18,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":6,"hour":9,"minute":0},"close":{"day":6,"hour":18,"minute":0}}],"weekdayDescriptions":["Monday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Saturday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM","Sunday: Closed"],"nextOpenTime":"2026-02-12T14:00:00Z"},"userRatingCount":122,"displayName":{"text":"Main Square Dental","languageCode":"en"},"reviews":[{"name":"places/ChIJc-W9TRbM1IkRfrv7IR-gtT0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5U1JXZDBhR1JUWDFob1JreHRPRzA0TnpJMlpGRRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"5 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"I have been a patient of Dr. Malik’s dental clinic for over 8 years, and I can truly say it has been an exceptional experience throughout. Dr. Malik is not only an outstanding dentist with remarkable skill and expertise, but also someone who genuinely cares about his patients’ comfort and well-being. His calm and reassuring approach always puts me at ease, no matter the treatment.\nEqually, his wonderful team — Jaga, Shirin, and Suman — deserve special recognition. They are professional, kind, and attentive, creating such a welcoming atmosphere that every visit feels seamless. From scheduling appointments to the actual care in the chair, their dedication and warmth never go unnoticed.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"I have been a patient of Dr. Malik’s dental clinic for over 8 years, and I can truly say it has been an exceptional experience throughout. Dr. Malik is not only an outstanding dentist with remarkable skill and expertise, but also someone who genuinely cares about his patients’ comfort and well-being. His calm and reassuring approach always puts me at ease, no matter the treatment.\nEqually, his wonderful team — Jaga, Shirin, and Suman — deserve special recognition. They are professional, kind, and attentive, creating such a welcoming atmosphere that every visit feels seamless. From scheduling appointments to the actual care in the chair, their dedication and warmth never go unnoticed.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Saba St","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107028644136548117015/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ5ljMcAWy_T8_IAN3wOMzvFlIapAD28iitXGcmOqkD0Ls9Uw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"},"publishTime":"2025-09-04T00:07:35.931522395Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5U1JXZDBhR1JUWDFob1JreHRPRzA0TnpJMlpGRRAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5U1JXZDBhR1JUWDFob1JreHRPRzA0TnpJMlpGRRAB!2m1!1s0x89d4cc164dbde573:0x3db5a01f21fbbb7e"},{"name":"places/ChIJc-W9TRbM1IkRfrv7IR-gtT0/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUMtclB1SHpRRRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"3 years ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"Dr. Malik is the heart of this dental clinic, very professional, caring, well spoken and articulate. I always get my family appointments with him and rest is history. Never had any issues with his advice, meds or staff.\nAppointments are easy to get, the parking is paid parking for the street but one can always park at sobeys for short periods or side streets if anything. The place is clean, professional and always a joy to be at. Keep it up fellas.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"Dr. Malik is the heart of this dental clinic, very professional, caring, well spoken and articulate. I always get my family appointments with him and rest is history. Never had any issues with his advice, meds or staff.\nAppointments are easy to get, the parking is paid parking for the street but one can always park at sobeys for short periods or side streets if anything. The place is clean, professional and always a joy to be at. Keep it up fellas.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Naeem M Khan","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102145146042226115872/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWjRdDft1vVW7i9xUNT2BkE6PZbOXl_cGnPV6gL5HkOMJwEeVN5IQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7"},"publishTime":"2022-10-29T04:12:36.141794Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUMtclB1SHpRRRAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUMtclB1SHpRRRAB!2m1!1s0x89d4cc164dbde573:0x3db5a01f21fbbb7e"},{"name":"places/ChIJc-W9TRbM1IkRfrv7IR-gtT0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkU2FGWlJiVlJqZUVSYVMwSkZXWHB2UzNwd1dXYxAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"a week ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"I've been in this dental clinic for the last 10 years doctors the staffs of the best I recommend for the people this best service","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"I've been in this dental clinic for the last 10 years doctors the staffs of the best I recommend for the people this best service","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Habte Lakew","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100071412599562362712/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJAF3dH7Rc9530LyfgEVfjmtuYSDuzqRv7-S_srP09nveqzgQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2026-01-31T13:50:23.336111312Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkU2FGWlJiVlJqZUVSYVMwSkZXWHB2UzNwd1dXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkU2FGWlJiVlJqZUVSYVMwSkZXWHB2UzNwd1dXYxAB!2m1!1s0x89d4cc164dbde573:0x3db5a01f21fbbb7e"},{"name":"places/ChIJc-W9TRbM1IkRfrv7IR-gtT0/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUNJLTZTUHd3RRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"10 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"Dr. Malik and his team at Main Square Dental are very friendly and professional. They explain everything clearly and make sure I feel comfortable during my visit. The clinic is clean, well-organized, and the staff is always welcoming and caring, which makes my whole experience pleasant and stress-free. May Allah bless Dr. Malik and his team for their kindness and excellent service. Thank you.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"Dr. Malik and his team at Main Square Dental are very friendly and professional. They explain everything clearly and make sure I feel comfortable during my visit. The clinic is clean, well-organized, and the staff is always welcoming and caring, which makes my whole experience pleasant and stress-free. May Allah bless Dr. Malik and his team for their kindness and excellent service. Thank you.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Saira Sultana","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116016245578838188520/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxTr2zia99E6N0SvFwVSZniWSWllCYNqeUi6-h__YFmL0oFB5kOQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2025-04-05T00:58:17.219630Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUNJLTZTUHd3RRAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUNJLTZTUHd3RRAB!2m1!1s0x89d4cc164dbde573:0x3db5a01f21fbbb7e"},{"name":"places/ChIJc-W9TRbM1IkRfrv7IR-gtT0/reviews/ChZDS